description: For sale: $865,000. The masterfully crafted exterior with extensive landscaping, over sized turn around driveway, 7 car garage and front stone archway welcome you to the dramatic floor to ceiling windows that capture the picturesque 3 acres of privacy and sunset views.  11 foot ceilings showcase the gleaming Maple woodwork, new carpet, stone fireplace and built ins.  Enjoy preparing dinner in the gourmet kitchen with granite countertops, oversized island, double oven, 5 burner gas cooktop, pull out drawers and a walk in pantry.  All living facilities are on one level including the executive master suite, walk in closet and en suite bath. Relax in your screened in porch with trex decking, cedar roof and a gas stove.  Entertain in your walkout lower level equipped with a palatial wet bar and billiard room.  The 7 stall garage is a car enthusiasts dream with 3 attached stalls fully insulated and heated and the upper level detached 4 car also heated and insulated both with storage and floor drains.

For sale: $685,000. Simply breathtaking inside and out!! Light, bright, open and flowing floorplan with hardwood floors, enameled millwork, and gorgeous selections! Well-appointed kitchen opens to sun filled living spaces with windows at every turn! Idyllic five acre setting boasts abundant landscaping, hundreds of trees, fenced in raised garden beds with raspberry bushes and apple and pear trees.  The extra large maintenance free deck is perfect for large outdoor gatherings.  The heated 32 x 28 pole barn has a 2nd floor man cave and a 20' work bench.   A storage shed close to the garden could also be used as a adorable kids playhouse with loft.  The possibilities are endless. There is something for everyone! A must see!  Take a minute to take the virtual tour and feel at home.

description: For sale: $400,000. Spacious home on over 3 acres and tucked into many mature trees for the utmost in privacy.  The backyard backs up to a pond and wetland area - enjoy stunning views and an abundance of wildlife all year round.  The large Living Room features brand new carpeting and a big bay window.  The open Kitchen has been extensively remodeled in 2020 with new granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, backsplash, and flooring.  French doors lead you into the sunny Four Season Porch offering panoramic views of the pond, wetland, and lush woods.  Your Master Suite features His and Her closets plus a private bath.  Cozy up to the stone, gas fireplace in the walkout lower level Family Room.  Relax in the Jacuzzi tub in the lower level bath.  An oversized garage offers a built-in workbench and a service door to the backyard.  There is so much more to see!  Check out the supplement for a complete list of updates/upgrades!

description: For sale: $529,900. Impeccably maintained, custom built log home on private, wooded, beautifully landscaped 2.5 acres! Several areas to enjoy the serene setting including the 3 seasons screened in porch and spacious deck. Home is surrounded by trees and overlooks open pasture for ultimate privacy. Stunning stone, wood burning fireplace grabs your attention as you enter the home. Gourmet kitchen features granite counters and stainless steel appliances. Main floor master bedroom has private office, large walk-in closet, and spacious bathroom. Finish the lower level to add 1500+ of living space! Oversized 2 car garage. This home is a must see!

For sale: $397,000. This 1900 Farmhouse sits on a sprawling 10 acres with a 60x36 barn with 6 stalls ready for horses, a 48x24 garage and a machine shed. This home is filled with traditional charm and so much character. Kitchen is huge with room for a dining set and there is a formal dining room where you can cozy up to the wood burning stove. The large family room is rustic with its pine ceiling, perfect for entertaining, the 3 season porch is great for relaxing in the evening and enjoy your morning coffee on the front porch. Beautiful country living only minutes from shopping and restaurants. Welcome Home!

description: For sale: $999,900. Incredible 6,000 plus square foot custom built walkout two story, situated on 12.27 gated acres overlooking two ponds and two tree farms!  This home is an entertainer's dream with two, 4-season porches, relaxing hot tub, and a wine room. This home is meticulously kept with exquisite detail and an interior that will not disappoint! The 4 bed/4 bath, 5 fireplace estate showcases custom woodwork & cabinetry, Cambria countertops, Wolf stove, high-end finishing's. Basement renovated in 2019, main/upper floor in 2018. Impressive private owner's suite with two walk-in closets, walk-in shower, jacuzzi tub, and many more upgrades!  Pole shed added in 2017, exterior of home and detached garage is LP siding, authentic stone, lawn irrigated and asphalt driveway. Detached garage has extra living space/business space with fireplace.

description: For sale: $394,900. RARE one owner custom built home situated on 2 acres with pond views.  Enjoy the peace and tranquility of living on a dead end road with the home oriented to where you do not see any neighbors! Updated 4 bedroom + office, 4 bathrooms, 3 family rooms, and a divine 3 season porch! Abundance of natural light throughout. All electrical has been updated and brought to code, radon mitigation system installed, brand new deck and retaining wall, new appliances including dishwasher, washer machine and oven! Water test has been preformed and passed. Septic system has been inspection and drain field passed and a new 1,500 septic tank is being installed as soon as road restrictions are lifted. Over-sized attached garage with expansive mud room PLUS an additional detached garage and shed! Spectacular yard with expansive deck and several flower and vegetable gardens. Geothermal heat and a/c as well as forced. This is truly a one of a kind home you won't want to miss out on!

description:
Recently sold: $474,900. The Exceptional Home Team is collecting food shelf donations to support Interfaith Outreach! During the month of April stop by anyone of our open houses with your donations. Some of the most needed items include diapers, canned fruit, peanut butter, jelly, dish/laundry soap, toilet paper, paper towels and toiletries.
Stunning home on 4+ acres. 40 minutes from downtown and less than 1 mile to Lake Sara. This beautiful home features a very large entry, a main level open concept floor plan, vaulted ceilings, maple floors, stone fireplace, walk-in pantry, newly remodeled kitchen with granite counters and mosaic tile backsplash. Sliding glass doors in dining room lead out spacious deck. Master bedroom has a 4 piece en suite with whirlpool tub and private balcony! Walkout lower level with 4 bedrooms. Security system and radon system. 2,000 square feet outbuilding, lot allows for 1 horse!

Recently sold: $292,500. Pride in ownership! Immaculate 4BR, 2BA home on nearly one acre! Fantastic fenced yard includes gorgeous landscaping, mature trees, in ground pool & a 22x14 barn style shed for storage. This meticulously maintained home is priced to sell, so do not miss out!

Recently sold: $775,000. 10 Minutes from Medina! Executive style two story in private setting! Enjoy beautiful lake views and maple trees in the wooded back yard retreat. Open floor plan with custom design kitchen with 2 sub zero refrigerators and a wolf range with indoor grill. Home office on main level with fireplace. Room to expand in the lower level partially finished basement with 9ft ceilings "over 6,000 sq. ft with finished basement!" Convenient commute to Minneapolis as well as only 15 min to shopping in downtown Plymouth, Maple Grove and Ridgedale.  Acres of fun and a back yard built for entertaining.  Large flagstone fire-pit. 3 private schools close by. Horse boarding and miles of trails nearby! Public access to 2 lakes with great fishing within 1.5 miles. Heated 4+ car garage, to store all your toys. 3 zone heating. 400 amp service. Saltwater pool with auto cover equals low maintenance. Stamped concrete driveway, patio, and pool deck. Motivated Sellers! Bring Offers!

description:
Recently sold: $378,000. Long Beautiful Views of Jubert Lake and Countryside
MAIN LEVEL

Foyer
Welcoming you into the home is the large tiled foyer. It has plenty of space to move around, a door leading to the garage, and a large walk-in closet.

Living Room
Coming up the stairs is a welcoming living room with vaulted ceilings, massive picture windows, carpet, and open to the informal dining room.

Informal Dining Room
Open to the kitchen and living room, the informal dining room has the continuing vaulted ceiling and a large window allowing for natural light. 

Kitchen
The kitchen boasts spacious granite counters, a breakfast bar, a large pantry, a built-in desk, and plenty of cabinet space.

4-Season Porch 
The 4-season porch is gorgeous and a warming place to hang out and enjoy the views. It contains a gas fireplace, a vaulted knotty pine ceiling, carpet, windows surrounding the entire room (including trapezoid windows), a ceiling fan, recessed lighting, and a sliding glass door leading to the deck and backyard.
Master Bedroom 
The master has a large double closet, carpet, ceiling fan, and a walk-through full tiled bath.
Bedroom 2
The second bedroom is carpeted, has a large window, and is located adjacent to the full bathroom.
LOWER LEVEL
Family Room 
A perfect place for entertaining! This family room is carpeted, has wainscoting around the room, and large windows.


Bedroom 3 & 4
The lower level bedrooms are large, carpeted, windows allowing for plenty of light, closets, and located conveniently next to a large ¾ tiled bathroom with a large linen closet. 

Additional Features:
?	Breathtaking Views
?	Large 3-Car Second Garage
?	Air to Air Exchanger
?	Laundry Tub
?	Vaulted Ceilings Throughout
?	Award Winning School District (Delano)
?	New Central A/C
?	Almost Everything in Kitchen is 1 Year Old
?	Lower Level Newly Painted
